        "text": [
          "ه عن ابن أبي نجران فقد رويته عن أبي- رضي اللّه عنه- عن سعد ابن عبد اللّه، عن أحمد بن محمّد بن عيسى، عن عبد الرّحمن بن أبي نجران‌."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Ibn Abi Najran has been transmitted by me from my father - may Allah (swt) be pleased with him - from Sad ibn Abdullah, from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa, from Abd Al-Rahman ibn Abi Najran."
